{"tid":1889963,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［有料驚閪］疫情打亂安排　星、港金融公司推遲招聘","createTime":"2020-02-21T01:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T04:15:15.000Z","uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7424063522fa3de1a2fb37225052379605247687","tid":1889963,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T01:57:42.000Z","msg":"外媒報道，由於新冠肺炎疫情打亂業務，位於新加坡和香港的金融公司正推遲招聘。<br />\n<br />\n據報，這兩個金融中心的獵頭公司表示，本地和外資機構紛紛放緩了招聘步伐。而影響因素包括部分人員須隔離、來往中國旅遊受限、遠程工作安排以及須不進行「面對面」的面試等。此外，疫情之下工廠關閉、供應鏈受到阻礙，部分公司指商業惡化影響收入，招聘已不是當務之急。<br />\n<br />\n據顧問公司Morgan McKinley董事總經理Gurj Sandhu稱，人們的注意力已經不在招聘之上，不過迄今還沒有公司取消招聘的職位。<br />\n<br />\n財經媒體彭博與六家招聘公司進行了交談，均證實招聘放緩。由於後勤方面存在困難，大多數公司的招聘流程和員工遷移計劃都要花上更長的時間。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200220/mobile/bkn-20200220102949846-0220_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200220%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200220102949846-0220_00842_001.html&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqF%2BQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=cd8cd660\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200220/mobile/bkn-20200220102949846-0220_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61547e64613e3f952b14a5865394db98b0ee5c43","tid":1889963,"uid":94007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T04:15:15.000Z","msg":"仲請人咩,加下唔撚比人炒都算偷笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}